    "name": "Infinite Widgets",
    "steam_appid": 1743370,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743370/extras/ae9726f97abfcabfce6e1a40c8d4bda9.avif?t=1758116753\" width=616 height=240 /></span><strong>提升您的桌面体验，使用 Infinite Widgets，这款终极软件可以创建自定义小部件，显示您所需的所有信息。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>使用 Infinite Widgets 创建、共享或下载小部件，提升您的桌面用户体验。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743370/extras/43d6a4d95a94970cf9f0a65c12b62431.webp?t=1758116753\" width=700 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>软件开发者？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >借助我们内置的渲染器和 Lua 支持，您可以创建独特的小部件，满足您的特定需求。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>更倾向于网页开发？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们的 JavaScript 集成允许您创建具有与 Lua 实现相同深度的基于网页的小部件！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lua 和 JavaScript 之间的通信是可能的，这使得构建复杂的交互式小部件变得更加容易。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>不是开发者？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们的编辑器允许您无需编码即可创建小部件！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对于那些感兴趣的人，使用 Infinite Widgets 学习编程可以是一次有趣且有益的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743370/extras/4c8ec5a9a665446d48e299eb7ed648f5.webp?t=1758116753\" width=700 height=55 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>实时监控</strong>：显示详细的系统性能信息。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743370/extras/a7869c0a46194edc1b29e7606f98568b.avif?t=1758116753\" width=480 height=336 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>媒体支持</strong>：显示和控制您系统上播放的音乐。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743370/extras/595fe8eaf19f516342cb5a92540c6836.avif?t=1758116753\" width=299 height=384 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>窗口停靠</strong>：创建具有保留监视器工作区域的小部件。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743370/extras/f375e4b05672500a623f5462d04e04d1.avif?t=1758116753\" width=415 height=611 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>停靠和任务栏</strong>：创建您自己的 Windows 停靠或任务栏小部件。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743370/extras/0c1d385defc0e0985669ab0562588efa.avif?t=1758116753\" width=406 height=115 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Steam 集成</strong>：启动 Steam 游戏，查看游戏缩略图，访问您最近和最常玩的游戏。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743370/extras/23297a33e5ccae087975860379628e0f.avif?t=1758116753\" width=444 height=390 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>固定或不固定</strong>：创建固定在桌面的小部件或覆盖在其他所有小部件上的小部件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多个视图</strong>：同时运行同一小部件的多个实例。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>存储</strong>：小部件可以保存和检索自定义数据。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>想要更多？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发现多种工具，创建您独特的小部件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743370/extras/a558c932e873fcd82db701bf64c6cc95.avif?t=1758116753\" width=404 height=403 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743370/extras/2a4121442de68a876c7a0e40d6f5170b.webp?t=1758116753\" width=700 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>担心性能？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Infinite Widgets 的处理器使用率非常低，确保不会干扰您的计算机性能或游戏体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743370/extras/c530446b2c729f21597cef4d1ee454f7.webp?t=1758116753\" width=700 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>需要帮助入门？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们提供示例小部件以及关于使用我们的 Lua 和 JavaScript 实现的内置全面文档，以及编辑器的关键元素，确保您拥有充分的信息，充分利用 Infinite Widgets！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用 Infinite Widgets，您的桌面将既实用又时尚。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
